### Hadith 2:667

*Narrated 'Abis bin Rabia:*

'Umar came near the Black Stone and kissed it and said "No doubt, I know
that you are a stone and can neither benefit anyone nor harm anyone. Had
I not seen Allah's Apostle kissing you I would not have kissed you."

